    Response for a merchant record on the gateway.

    The following values will be present in ALL Merchant Responses:

    • setId(String)
    • setName(String)
    The following values will only be present if the merchant is using MerchantPartners gateway.
    • setMerchantPartnersId(String)
    • setMerchantPartnersPin(String)

    The following values will only be present if the merchant is using SecureNet gateway.

    • setSecureNetId(String)
    • setSecureNetKey(String)
    • setSecureNetPublicKey(String)

    The following values will only be present if the merchant is using PassMarket as their loyalty service provider.

    • setPassMarketKey(String)
    • setPassMarketSecret(String)
